task.persona: A claims adjuster experienced in handling property damage claims for handymen

instruction.level1: Schedule a meeting on May 20th to discuss the status of pending property damage claims
instruction.level2: Schedule a meeting on May 20, 2025, to discuss the status of pending property damage claims.
instruction.level3: Schedule a meeting titled 'Discussion on Pending Property Damage Claims' on May 20, 2025, from 4:00 PM to 5:00 PM.

steps: Click the 'Create' button to start creating a new event.
Click the 'Event' menu item to continue creating a new event.
Fill in the event title with 'Discussion on Pending Property Damage Claims'.
Click the date and time button to edit the event start date.
Fill in the start date with 'Tuesday, May 20, 2025'
Fill in the start time with '4:00 PM'.
Fill in the end time with '5:00 PM' for the event.
Click the 'Save' button to finalize creating the event.
